rc=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T07:26:31.000Z","msg":"漏咗特權階層呀巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n500人聚集passing out<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201213/T2WHFMBSM5CI5KIN6PZSFRTLCQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201213%2FT2WHFMBSM5CI5KIN6PZSFRTLCQ%2F&d=Yr0hxYoWOJ9ZaoTMuy4WzJggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=ef89d9e9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201213%2FT2WHFMBSM5CI5KIN6PZSFRTLCQ%2F&h=97571e7b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201213/T2WHFMBSM5CI5KIN6PZSFRTLCQ/</a><br />\n國慶群組<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200818/47L4VTW2LZCBZF474ONCVY7BQM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200818%2F47L4VTW2LZCBZF474ONCVY7BQM%2F&d=Yr0hxYoWOJ9ZaoTMuy4WzJggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=09e2168f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200818%2F47L4VTW2LZCBZF474ONCVY7BQM%2F&h=2a63a8ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200818/47L4VTW2LZCBZF474ONCVY7BQM/</a>"},{"pid":"21bfacbc59747c7d60aae3c96eae9f85d02e90b2","tid":2334273,"uid":344824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ba3e8bda230fd126a49fc112f13058f0ccb661b","tid":2334273,"uid":367255,"like":52,"dislike":1,"score":51,"quote":{"pid":"d636909de838f7201581af906606ba10267e3154","tid":2334273,"uid":60744,"like":65,"dislike":1,"score":64,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T05:23:13.000Z","msg":"幾時限返工"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T05:24:39.000Z","msg":"問過黎生未？ <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aaoYZCH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaaoYZCH.jpg&h=7d6d399f&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T07:27:58.000Z","msg":"黎字派浦頭"},{"pid":"bebcf1f1629be92de2627b7892e7c94a048f9f04","tid":2334273,"uid":123195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44c1b9ab188933957a108f88ee100c05914133e2","tid":2334273,"uid":56428,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"c253406502a148111b584be635937182d33cdf4c","tid":2334273,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T05:22:43.000Z","msg":"本港新冠肺炎疫情嚴峻，呼吸系統專科醫生梁子超今日（21日）表示，第四波疫情的不明源頭個案有上升趨勢，認為並不樂觀，他批評過去周末商場及元朗大棠人頭湧湧，「只能用恐怖嚟形容」。政府專家顧問、港大感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良亦指，一旦放寛社交距離措施，確診數字恐創新高，如有家庭聚會群組爆發，不排除仿英國限制家庭聚會。<br />\n<br />\n梁子超：病毒深入本港任何角落 <br />\n梁子超接受港台節目《千禧年代》訪問時表示，現時本港仍有不少不明源頭個案，過去一周有216宗不明源頭個案，較對上一周212宗有升勢，情況並不樂觀。梁稱第四波相比第三波更嚴峻，第三波數字上落迅速，但第四波不明源頭個案處於高位仍有輕微升勢，「係唔好嘅徵兆」。<br />\n<br />\n梁指病毒已深入本港任何角落，在不同聚集場合、家庭、樓宇、醫療設施等即使佩戴了口罩，或做了手衞生都有感染機會，勸籲市民除了上班減少外出，切勿奢望有靈丹妙藥，否則無法控制疫情，「過去兩日商場同郊野公園聚集情況，只能用恐怖嚟形容」。<br />\n<br />\n至於是否要採取宵禁等更嚴厲措施，梁認為，疫情已滲入角落，不能在香港經濟民生崩潰前控制疫情，政府應宣揚更強硬訊息，加強執法，否則會如美國感恩節假期後反彈一樣。<br />\n<br />\n何栢良：若放寬現時社交距離  確診數字恐創新高<br />\n何栢良在同一節目指出，應維持現行社交距離措施，一旦放寛恐創新高，現時每日近百個案，過去每天平均30多宗源頭不明個案，如有需要不排除任何措施，正如英國都有限制家庭聚會。<br />\n<br />\n何栢良在商台節目《在晴朗的一天出發》指出，接下來聖誕節部分市民或會狂歡，確診個字或高處未算高，「會唔會過完聖誕，三、四百宗 其實係唔出奇。」他亦呼籲市民要自救，「政府能力就係咁多，要10日8日先送到入醫院。你想佢短時間內變到超人係做唔到，市民要諗辦法自救。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201219/416988510189522944736129.jpeg/gcYHr4IIC02VrqWLJaPde2Muh_-s4TTsUpDntVKQ57U?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201219%2F416988510189522944736129.jpeg%2FgcYHr4IIC02VrqWLJaPde2Muh_-s4TTsUpDntVKQ57U%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=fe4b206f&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T05:30:14.000Z","msg":"點解唔限番工？ 講到病毒咁勁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T07:29:39.000Z","msg":"限制埋出糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5451d0b87136bd5d8fd7b9d0f879dd6e2fd05d9f","tid":2334273,"uid":8426,"like